file_name": "Drum Circle Cover Art (2560 x 1440 px) (1).png", "id": "1161447404916858", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982625_1161447408250191_2650284731583729103_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=aDp8MobjBEsQ7kNvgFII7_x&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDmzkzVGsR2raumXgWLAxp0fZQEtKzZv8kRCJg6BlqYfA&oe=67752482"}, "display_name": "Drum Circle", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Unleash your inner musician with *Drum Circle*! Step into a vibrant virtual world where you can play a variety of instruments using just your hands. Whether you're grooving on the conga drums, tapping out rhythms on the bongos, creating melodies on a keyboard, or shaking maracas to the beat, *Drum Circle* brings the joy of music-making to life in immersive VR.\n\n**Features:**\n- Play a range of instruments: congas, bongos, keyboards, and maracas!\n- Play along with *music tracks* or create your own rhythms and melodies\n- Intuitive hand-tracking lets you perform naturally without controllers.\n\nGet ready to feel the rhythm, unleash your creativity, and make music like never before with *Drum Circle*!", "short_description": "Unleash your inner musician with Drum Circle! Step into a vibrant virtual world where you can play a variety of instruments using just your hands. Whether you're grooving on the conga drums, tapping out rhythms on the bongos, creating melodies on a keyboard, or shaking maracas to the beat, Drum Circle brings the joy of music-making to life in immersive VR."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://artisanreality.com/privacy-policy-for-drum-circle", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Artisan Effects", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://artisanreality.com/drum-circle", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topic